html:
7.30.25  3:42 am   should i meet strangers?

      maybe sometimes

7.30.25  3:35 am   you seem to have been quite fond of the 'other / prefer not to say' answer in the past month or so. is this a new thing or did you rediscover an old thing?

      i'm surprised i didn't think of using that earlier. i've seen it on official forms and it shines like gold on there

7.30.25  2:10 am   i keep re-doing parts of a long-term project i'm working on. in the beginning, i used to write little writeups about what i was doing for the project so i felt like i had something to release. now i don't want to writeup anything because i feel like everything is just going to be replaced when i decide i have a better idea later on. i feel like what's the point of working if i'm just going to replace whatever i'm working on. i know logically that's it's getting better, but emotionally i feel kaput. i did some little side projects to recharge my battery but now i'm back to this and i'm afraid. help??! also how do i know if i'm making progress or going crazy

      basically you wanna start looking forward to your birthday party when you finally move on from this project, taking the lessons with you

7.30.25  1:39 am   do you think our attention spans are actually getting worse? 

      no, this recurring empty complaint is simply a timeless tradition

7.30.25  1:24 am   how to come back from ruining my life?

      how about a sort of re birth

7.30.25  1:19 am   What do you think about paying taxes

      it doesn't always say on the receipt what you're paying for. so i can understand why that may cause some confusion for some people

7.30.25  12:18 am   Do you believe in the existence of the belief of existence of belief :)?

      let me perform some calculations

7.30.25  12:06 am   what is your favorite musical

      i'm trying to imagine what that would even be like

7.30.25  12:01 am   is my age a good age or is it one of the bad ones i can't tell

      it's good

7.29.25  10:15 pm   have you ever acted in someone else's project?

      no

7.29.25  9:59 pm   Let's do all the things so that we can rest later

      how many things do you think there are

7.29.25  9:28 pm   How do you build and keep artistic momentum

      almost as if by surprise

7.29.25  6:47 pm   how androgynous are you?

      i couldn't even begin to calculate

7.29.25  5:34 pm   You dont know me, I dont know you. I am going to Uni soon, any tips on how to better enjoy what is new?

      it will be easier to enjoy once it actually happens. just studying what you've said here, it seems you are talking about an upcoming point in the future

7.29.25  5:17 pm   do you have an internal monologue?

      yes, sometimes also external

7.29.25  4:59 pm   are you super cool?

      only when absolutely necessary

7.29.25  3:10 pm   Should NYC be pronounced like Nick?

      could work

7.29.25  2:51 pm   have you felt a feeling of stillness recently? what was it like?

      not exactly

7.29.25  1:13 pm   So my friends and I made this joke band and got together and wrote/recorded an entire joke song on our first session.
But after that, we suddenly don't feel the drive anymore, no inspiration
I felt like I motivated and kinda guided them through the whole thing, but now suddenly im too self conscious and dont know how to replicate it.
do you have any advice?????

      what makes you think you are supposed to do the same thing again

7.29.25  12:42 pm   any tips to not go insane?

      start working on something. it almost doesn't even matter what it is

7.29.25  11:35 am   whats your favourite type of triangle

      scalene

7.29.25  11:09 am   Do you think Da Vinci looked back on his art and though, "I wish that one turned out better."

      i don't know anything about da vinci, but that is a perfectly reasonable and probable thought for any artist to have from time to time

7.29.25  10:15 am   How did you because the musical genius that you are today, and how do you continue to be that same musical genius in the future 

      basically it's about getting up on the wrong side of the bed on purpose

7.29.25  6:25 am   I have so many schoolworks, what do I do with them?

      how about putting them in order, just to see what you're dealing with

7.29.25  6:16 am   would you mind providing me with a little bit of encouragement

      encouragement is free and it's everywhere, but that admittedly sounds like empty advice without any specifics given for me to lend it towards

7.29.25  5:42 am   do you prefer multitasking between several projects or doing just one through to completion?

      if there is a plan, then the plan itself can be the project even if it involves multiple parts

7.29.25  4:59 am   how to do things despite being moderately tired? organisation- and timing-wise buying groceries now is the better move but the feeling in my arms and legs is persuading me not to go

      sounds like the memory of the consequences of not going is fading. when was the last time you found out what happens when you don't go?

7.29.25  4:49 am   Do you think we'll run out of music one day? Like, do you think one day every possible song will have been written?

      no

7.29.25  2:56 am   Do you ever have thoughts that seem cool but you don't understand what they mean?

      of course. that's part of probably a typical day for any artist

7.29.25  2:41 am   opinion on the colour green

      it's really good, but all the colors are really good

7.29.25  2:32 am   How often do you think about being an animal?

      not that often

7.29.25  1:19 am   Why is bacon called bacon when you cook it, and why are cookies called cookies when you bake them?

      because you are looking for interesting patterns in language

7.29.25  12:43 am   best decade?

      how about the next 10 years starting right now

7.29.25  12:31 am   do you enjoy spending time answering these questions?

      sometimes, whereas also other times i may enjoy answering them extremely fast

7.29.25  12:23 am   why don't just all the shops in the world become one big shop so no one goes out of business?

      so crazy it just might work

7.28.25  10:58 pm   you ever play mario kart?

      sure but i don't like switching to a different game every time

7.28.25  10:57 pm   i feel like you've changed recently. do you know what i mean or am i hallucinating this

      not any more than i usually change, which is hopefully a fair amount, but, what you're perceiving at this moment is more of a change in yourself

7.28.25  10:16 pm   Will your newer videos feature more shots of you dancing in front of a green screen

      of course, but also sometimes things other than that

7.28.25  9:51 pm   bill you truly are a really cool guy. can i have some pizza

      i don't have any pizza to give away, but you can still have some as long as you find it yourself

7.28.25  9:30 pm   Are you actually a huge gamer most of the time? What games do you usually choose? 

      i thought that story was about you

7.28.25  8:38 pm   Do you keep up with trends or do you prefer to avoid/not care about them.

      now you've got me wondering who gets to be the person upto whom everyone else is trying to keep

7.28.25  8:27 pm   hi im in class rn should i keep procrastinating 

      sure

7.28.25  7:49 pm   do you eat the core of the apple? 

      i don't believe i've ever done that

7.28.25  6:44 pm   why do you have a webpage answering random questions from random anonymous strangers?

      maybe it's a way to make up for an extreme lack of correspondence elsewhere in my life and career

7.28.25  6:02 pm   what do you think of the Airport Terminal as allegory for life and birth

      isn't everything

7.28.25  5:54 pm   what's a lie i can tell my friends?

      how about something you just looked up on the internet

7.28.25  5:52 pm   chess or checkers?

      is there a horsey

7.28.25  5:45 pm   hey bill , whats ur fav band of of all time?

      i'm trying to think of what that would even be like

7.28.25  5:33 pm   how to make every single person on earth angry

      i don't think that's possible

7.28.25  5:12 pm   Why is the speed of light is so unfair to the speed of sound? Where's the equality?

      if everything in the world went the exact same speed, there would be no such thing as speed
